  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        - Subjects aged 18 years and above with complete division of the Flexor Digitorum Profundus
        (FDP) tendon in Zone II.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects with additional complicated injuries

          -  Subjects whose flexor tendon repair involves a finger with less than full tendon
             function prior to the injury requiring repair

          -  Subjects who are undergoing surgical repair of the severed tendon(s) more than four
             days after the injury occurred.

          -  Subjects with a history of clinical significant hypersensitivity to any of the
             devices, drugs or surgical dressings to be used in this trial.

          -  Subjects with conditions which may delay healing.

          -  Subjects who are taking, or have taken, any investigational drugs within 3 months
             prior to the screening visit.

          -  Females who are pregnant
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
